課程概述 Course Description
       統計機器學習與應用統計機器學習與應用    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
瞭解統計機器學習之理論基礎。熟悉常用的統計機器學習方法。使用R程式語言來整理/轉換/視覺化資料，並執行前述方法。 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Course Overview (CH1)2Overview of Statistical Learning (CH2)3Basic Knowledge in Matrix Algebra4Regression I: Linear Models (CH3)5Regression II: Extensions of Linear Models and KNN (CH3)6校際活動日停課一週7Classification I: Logistic Regression (CH4)8Classification II: Linear, Quadratic, and KNN Classifiers (CH4)9Resampling Method (CH5)10Model Selection I: Subset Selection (CH6)11Model Selection II: Ridge, Lasso, and Other Penalties (CH6)12Moving Beyond Linearity (CH7)13Support Vector Machine (CH9)14Tree-Based Methods (CH8)15Boosting and Ensemble Learning16Principal Component Analysis (CH10)17Cluster Analysis (CH10)18Final Competition 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


